{"tid":823293,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大交合我屌你老母！","createTime":"2018-09-16T18:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T09:18:32.000Z","uid":201299,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d54181fc4568fb56c47532ed64eff9cddcf328f","tid":823293,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"十二月，熱帶風暴布拉曼登陸越南，損失千萬；香港人在工作中。<br />\n二月，熱帶風暴三巴擊中菲律賓，共十四人死亡；香港人仍在OT中。<br />\n六月頭，熱帶風暴艾維尼吹襲中國南部，釀成五億損失；香港人放工迫地鐵回家。<br />\n六月尾，颱風巴比侖吹過日、韓，當地緊固建築亦抵受不住強風；香港人在食飯盒。<br />\n七月頭，颱風瑪莉亞吹襲台灣，當局宣佈停工停課；香港人打開電視機。<br />\n八月頭，颱風貝碧佳盤旋於華南沿岸上空；香港終於懸掛三號強風信號。<br />\n八月尾，颱風燕子吹襲日本，當地橋梁等基建倒塌；香港人對著電腦工作。<br />\n九月，颱風山竹橫掃廣東，深圳、澳門停工停課，港珠澳人工島陸沉；香港人仍謹記<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽朝準時返工</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n波台狗：個風濕濕碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc2a9054843717132ed48eb1073ce5b8393861c","tid":823293,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"依加出面仲好大雨 d風 fungfung聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971e1241cf9e2bb205bc8bbafed5fcf6d03eb1b4","tid":823293,"uid":20908,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/020550_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F020550_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=eba7c32f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2c79cf7a0fed7eda14f960fc44cac9790fc57f7","tid":823293,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dc2a9054843717132ed48eb1073ce5b8393861c","tid":823293,"